    "Linear and Gaussian activation functions were also reported, and they are used for regression problems.",
    "Learning Rate determines the step size toward finding the minimum loss value.",
    "The most common learning rate was 0.001, followed by 0.1, which was also the largest reported learning rate.",
    "Other less common values ranged from 1e -6 up to 0.05.",
    "Optimization Algorithm changes the network parameters to reduce the loss, and the Adam optimizer (Kingma and Ba, 2017) was almost exclusively used by all of the publications."
